This paper deals with optimization of a filter structure using Genetic Algorithm, which falls under the category of system and control (cs.SY). The paper also involves signal processing techniques for rational approximation of fractional order elements, which can be categorized under signal processing (cs.SI). The use of optimization techniques and algorithms also suggests a possibility of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG). The paper also involves numerical analysis and optimization, which can be categorized under numerical analysis (cs.NE) and computational engineering (cs.CE).
